# Add baseline renal function class

Add baseline renal function class

## Usage

``` r
add_bl_renal(obj, method = egfr_cg)
```

## Arguments

- obj:

  A NIF object.

- method:

  The function to calculate eGFR (CrCL) from serum creatinine. Currently
  either: egfr_mdrd, egfr_cg or egfr_raynaud

## Value

A NIF object.

## Examples
